1
00:00:05,840 --> 00:00:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's been three days since the festival...</i></font>

2
00:00:09,410 --> 00:00:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to watch the fireworks 
with just you, Eiyu!</font>

3
00:00:12,990 --> 00:00:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me too. I want to watch 
the fireworks with just you, Eiyu!</font>

4
00:00:20,180 --> 00:00:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But so far... nothing has happened.</i></font>

5
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:24,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f4f5f5"><font size="15">Shio</font></font></b></font>

6
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:24,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#dc959c"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="15">Festival Time!</font></font></font></b></font>

7
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:24,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="9"><font color="#bab9ba">Let's meet at 6 o'clock!</font></font></b></font>

8
00:00:21,880 --> 00:00:24,500
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="9"><font color="#7b976a">Roger</font></font></b></font>

9
00:00:25,210 --> 00:00:26,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm confused.</i></font>

10
00:00:26,500 --> 00:00:29,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Weren't we about to start a rom-com?!</i></font>

11
00:00:29,040 --> 00:00:30,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What happened?!</i></font>

12
00:00:30,070 --> 00:00:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What about the legend of love?</i></font>

13
00:00:31,440 --> 00:00:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Where?! Where did it all go?!</i></font>

14
00:00:32,260 --> 00:00:33,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Onii-chan!</font>

15
00:00:33,350 --> 00:00:34,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

16
00:00:39,980 --> 00:00:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here you go!</font>

17
00:00:43,990 --> 00:00:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks.</font>

18
00:00:45,890 --> 00:00:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You really don't mind paying?</font>

19
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I can pay you back 
with my allowance later.</font>

20
00:00:52,360 --> 00:00:55,030
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#7ba9f4">Used up his allowance at the festival...</font></font></font></b></font>

21
00:00:53,460 --> 00:00:55,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Don't worry about it!</font>

22
00:00:55,030 --> 00:00:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I couldn't make the festival,</font>

23
00:00:58,870 --> 00:01:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I'm so happy I get to go on a date 
with you today, Onii-chan!</font>

24
00:01:03,910 --> 00:01:05,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A date, huh?</font>

25
00:01:05,030 --> 00:01:07,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for your generosity.</font>

26
00:01:08,340 --> 00:01:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seem kinda down.</font>

27
00:01:10,030 --> 00:01:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did something happen at the festival?</font>

28
00:01:12,550 --> 00:01:13,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

29
00:01:15,490 --> 00:01:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing really happened...</font>

30
00:01:17,560 --> 00:01:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it turns out I was the only one 
looking forward to...</font>

31
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:28,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way my life would 
turn into some rom-com, right?</font>

32
00:01:28,540 --> 00:01:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will.</font>

33
00:01:29,420 --> 00:01:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

34
00:01:37,420 --> 00:01:38,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So sweet!</font>

35
00:01:38,500 --> 00:01:43,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know what happened, 
but it's always been one for me.</font>

36
00:01:44,380 --> 00:01:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's always been a rom-com.</font>

37
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

38
00:01:49,140 --> 00:01:52,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's always been a rom-com for me.</font>

39
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:57,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! Your heart just jumped, didn't it?</font>

40
00:01:59,060 --> 00:02:00,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha—?!</font>

41
00:02:00,200 --> 00:02:01,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?</font>

42
00:02:01,430 --> 00:02:03,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tease me like that.</font>

43
00:02:03,610 --> 00:02:05,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, that startled me.</font>

44
00:02:05,890 --> 00:02:10,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go get the food, 
so wait there, Onii-chan!</font>

45
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez! Why is everyone 
messing with me right now?</font>

46
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:19,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you're getting 
all the attention, as usual.</font>

47
00:02:19,330 --> 00:02:20,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

48
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

49
00:02:41,250 --> 00:02:44,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I think you must be 
mistaking me for someone else.</font>

50
00:02:44,020 --> 00:02:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

51
00:02:46,260 --> 00:02:48,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay! These are shorts!</font>

52
00:02:49,780 --> 00:02:50,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

53
00:02:51,300 --> 00:02:53,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, see ya later, Eiyu!</font>

54
00:02:54,740 --> 00:02:57,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why does she know my nickname?</font>

55
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:59,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan, do you know her?</font>

56
00:02:59,550 --> 00:03:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I don't think so...</font>

57
00:03:02,090 --> 00:03:03,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu...</font>

58
00:03:17,340 --> 00:03:22,470
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><font size="24"><b><font color="#0f100d">You Can't Be in a <font color="#29e1ef">Ro<font color="#ee3c51">m-<font color="#953db6">Co<font color="#f5a309">m <font color="#0f100d">with
Your Childhood Friends!</font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font></font></b></font>

59
00:04:35,860 --> 00:04:37,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're late!</font>

60
00:04:37,260 --> 00:04:39,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">School starts today, you know!</font>

61
00:04:39,300 --> 00:04:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that!</font>

62
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio, let's just leave him behind!</font>

63
00:04:44,630 --> 00:04:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Did you know a new cosmetics shop 
opened in the station building?</font>

64
00:04:46,180 --> 00:04:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're my childhood friends.</i></font>

65
00:04:47,460 --> 00:04:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, really?</font>

66
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:50,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Wanna go check it out?</font>

67
00:04:49,040 --> 00:04:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Summer break's over, and we're 
back to the same old routine.</i></font>

68
00:04:50,610 --> 00:04:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, let's go! When's a good time?</font>

69
00:04:53,300 --> 00:04:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As expected, you can't be in a rom-com 
with your childhood friends.</i></font>

70
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is <i>totally</i> a rom-com!</font>

71
00:05:01,470 --> 00:05:02,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's you again!</font>

72
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look at you, Eiyu!</font>

73
00:05:04,990 --> 00:05:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Walking with two beauties in the morning?</font>

74
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so jealous! Come here!</font>

75
00:05:11,030 --> 00:05:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What happened to the cutie 
from last time, huh?</font>

76
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:15,840
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#ef9bee">SQUEEZE</font></font></b></font>

77
00:05:14,260 --> 00:05:16,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Squish, squish, squish, squish!</font>

78
00:05:16,280 --> 00:05:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, let go of him!</font>

79
00:05:19,130 --> 00:05:20,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which "cutie"?</font>

80
00:05:21,460 --> 00:05:23,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was Runako.</font>

81
00:05:23,030 --> 00:05:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako?</font>

82
00:05:24,220 --> 00:05:26,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're telling me <i>that</i> was Runako?</font>

83
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:27,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah...</font>

84
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup.</font>

85
00:05:30,960 --> 00:05:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're Shio and Akari.</font>

86
00:05:33,320 --> 00:05:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all look completely different!</font>

87
00:05:35,310 --> 00:05:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, it feels so nostalgic 
when all four of us are together!</font>

88
00:05:38,230 --> 00:05:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

89
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:40,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

90
00:05:40,780 --> 00:05:41,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then!</font>

91
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Later!</font>

92
00:05:47,960 --> 00:05:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who was that?</font>

93
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Beats me.</font>

94
00:05:50,970 --> 00:05:52,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it true, Sakai?</font>

95
00:05:52,740 --> 00:05:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're seeing <i>three</i> girls at once?!</font>

96
00:05:55,020 --> 00:05:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

97
00:05:55,740 --> 00:05:56,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about?!</font>

98
00:05:56,910 --> 00:05:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't play dumb!</font>

99
00:05:58,230 --> 00:06:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're already messing around 
with both of your childhood friends!</font>

100
00:06:00,670 --> 00:06:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I hear you're involved 
with a girl in junior high, too!</font>

101
00:06:03,380 --> 00:06:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did you hear this?</font>

102
00:06:05,350 --> 00:06:09,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh? What a funny rumor.</font>

103
00:06:09,010 --> 00:06:13,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm</i> letting that <i>idiot</i> 
mess around with <i>me</i>?</font>

104
00:06:13,770 --> 00:06:16,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And he's seeing <i>two other girls</i> 
at the same time?</font>

105
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's <i>hilarious</i>.</font>

106
00:06:18,650 --> 00:06:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whose dreaming up 
these funny stories?</font>

107
00:06:24,140 --> 00:06:25,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gosh!</font>

108
00:06:25,450 --> 00:06:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with those rumors?!</font>

109
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:30,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hinata Haru-san from 
the P.E. department, huh?</font>

110
00:06:31,570 --> 00:06:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's a rising first-year track star 
and pretty popular in class.</font>

111
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:40,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seems like the rumors spread 
after she talked about us.</font>

112
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:40,210
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#fac749">BLAH</font></b></font>

113
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:40,210
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#fac749">BLAH</font></b></font>

114
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:40,210
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#b49dfb">WHAAAT!!</font></b></font>

115
00:06:40,210 --> 00:06:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That tan girl!</font>

116
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's those girls, right?</font>

117
00:06:42,900 --> 00:06:44,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder why...</font>

118
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}He's seeing three girls at once, right?</font>

119
00:06:44,320 --> 00:06:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it seems like she knows us.</font>

120
00:06:45,570 --> 00:06:47,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Yeah, that's crazy.</font>

121
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:49,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know her!</font>

122
00:06:49,220 --> 00:06:51,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Fine, then.</font>

123
00:06:51,520 --> 00:06:53,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go set her straight!</font>

124
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu!</font>

125
00:06:57,840 --> 00:06:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um...</font>

126
00:06:59,050 --> 00:07:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is H-Hinata-san here?</font>

127
00:07:02,140 --> 00:07:05,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru? She's probably having 
lunch at the clubroom.</font>

128
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:08,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He acts all high-and-mighty with us...</font>

129
00:07:05,900 --> 00:07:08,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Thank you very much.</font>

130
00:07:08,390 --> 00:07:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I appreciate your help.</font>

131
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now I'm worried.</font>

132
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's here, huh?</font>

133
00:07:17,030 --> 00:07:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

134
00:07:18,850 --> 00:07:19,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

135
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a moment?</font>

136
00:07:21,650 --> 00:07:23,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh! Hold on a sec!</font>

137
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:23,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa!</font>

138
00:07:31,690 --> 00:07:32,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry!</font>

139
00:07:32,690 --> 00:07:34,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's just you, Eiyu.</font>

140
00:07:34,920 --> 00:07:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

141
00:07:36,140 --> 00:07:38,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me change real quick. Just wait there.</font>

142
00:07:38,610 --> 00:07:39,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Okay!</font>

143
00:07:43,810 --> 00:07:45,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, come in.</font>

144
00:07:46,220 --> 00:07:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Excuse... me?!</font>

145
00:07:54,290 --> 00:07:56,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ouch...</font>

146
00:07:57,710 --> 00:07:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry!</font>

147
00:07:59,960 --> 00:08:02,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... So... I'm here because...</font>

148
00:08:03,760 --> 00:08:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

149
00:08:05,940 --> 00:08:08,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know you're being super rude, right?</font>

150
00:08:08,780 --> 00:08:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's fine.</font>

151
00:08:10,050 --> 00:08:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But why are you acting 
all distant like that?</font>

152
00:08:13,070 --> 00:08:15,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're friends, aren't we?</font>

153
00:08:15,810 --> 00:08:18,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Friends? I don't know about that...</font>

154
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

155
00:08:24,270 --> 00:08:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way...</font>

156
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:27,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't remember me?</font>

157
00:08:30,000 --> 00:08:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if Eiyu's okay.</font>

158
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we go check in?</font>

159
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good idea.</font>

160
00:08:35,330 --> 00:08:38,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't say he's the most experienced 
when it comes to talking to girls.</font>

161
00:08:40,930 --> 00:08:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he's totally fine with us!</i></font>

162
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:47,460
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="8"><font color="#5c8094">Track and Field Club</font></font></b></font>

163
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Seriously?</font>

164
00:08:47,460 --> 00:08:48,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that true?!</font>

165
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's true.</font>

166
00:08:53,760 --> 00:08:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then Eiyu...</font>

167
00:08:56,490 --> 00:08:58,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna try touching them?</font>

168
00:08:59,780 --> 00:09:01,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck are you doing?!</font>

169
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

170
00:09:03,040 --> 00:09:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you were going to 
set her straight!</font>

171
00:09:04,970 --> 00:09:07,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think 
you're doing right now?!</font>

172
00:09:07,110 --> 00:09:08,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't do that! It's a crime!</font>

173
00:09:08,740 --> 00:09:11,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, no... I tripped is all.</font>

174
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But forget that!</font>

175
00:09:12,710 --> 00:09:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Haru!</font>

176
00:09:13,720 --> 00:09:16,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru from Nishi Elementary!</font>

177
00:09:16,250 --> 00:09:17,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

178
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:19,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">From Nishi Elementary...?</font>

179
00:09:22,020 --> 00:09:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on! Is that it?</font>

180
00:09:22,430 --> 00:09:24,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's getting late!</font>

181
00:09:24,510 --> 00:09:26,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to go home!</font>

182
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Onii-chan!</font>

183
00:09:27,930 --> 00:09:29,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the final round! 
Just one more!</font>

184
00:09:31,780 --> 00:09:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! You're weak, Eiyu!</font>

185
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn it!</font>

186
00:09:36,630 --> 00:09:38,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Losers get what they get!</font>

187
00:09:39,770 --> 00:09:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Haru was the kid who was athletic 
and sassy, but really fun to be around.</i></font>

188
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:47,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We'd always run around 
until the sun went down.</i></font>

189
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Brace yourself!</font>

190
00:09:49,760 --> 00:09:52,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't make it too painful, Haru-kun!</font>

191
00:09:52,700 --> 00:09:56,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I remember Haru as my 
childhood friend who's a boy.</i></font>

192
00:09:58,040 --> 00:09:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way...</font>

193
00:09:59,500 --> 00:10:00,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru-kun was...</font>

194
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:03,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A girl this whole time?!</font>

195
00:10:05,140 --> 00:10:08,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No wonder. It all makes sense now.</font>

196
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back in first semester, 
I tried saying hey and was ignored.</font>

197
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:11,520
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#f6de54">Hey!</font></b></font>

198
00:10:11,380 --> 00:10:13,930
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#bf8dfa">Huh?</font></b></font>

199
00:10:12,460 --> 00:10:13,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? Sorry!</font>

200
00:10:15,160 --> 00:10:16,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that...</font>

201
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:18,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always thought you were a perv</font>

202
00:10:18,340 --> 00:10:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">since you'd always invite me to 
go pee or go take a bath together.</font>

203
00:10:22,880 --> 00:10:23,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait...</font>

204
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Weren't you referring to yourself as 
a boy back then, um, Haru-san...?</font>

205
00:10:28,450 --> 00:10:30,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be so formal, just call me Haru!</font>

206
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:33,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I grew up with a lot of brothers, 
so I was probably copying them.</font>

207
00:10:43,750 --> 00:10:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you keep looking away?</font>

208
00:10:47,050 --> 00:10:49,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it because now that 
you know I'm a girl,</font>

209
00:10:49,770 --> 00:10:52,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're thinking of me differently?</font>

210
00:10:53,020 --> 00:10:54,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, um...</font>

211
00:10:56,060 --> 00:10:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So sad!</font>

212
00:10:57,360 --> 00:11:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always thought you were my friend!</font>

213
00:11:00,030 --> 00:11:01,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No...</font>

214
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're all flustered! 
How are you so adorable?</font>

215
00:11:08,620 --> 00:11:09,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

216
00:11:10,710 --> 00:11:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This girl...</font>

217
00:11:12,330 --> 00:11:14,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's not like that. 
I was just a little surprised, that's all.</font>

218
00:11:14,860 --> 00:11:18,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right, right. I get it, I get it!</font>

219
00:11:18,710 --> 00:11:20,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-Haru-kun!</font>

220
00:11:22,590 --> 00:11:23,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So...</font>

221
00:11:23,490 --> 00:11:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-Anyway...</font>

222
00:11:25,250 --> 00:11:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to talk.</font>

223
00:11:26,810 --> 00:11:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

224
00:11:29,400 --> 00:11:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously?! That's the rumor?</font>

225
00:11:31,950 --> 00:11:36,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only said I was jealous since Eiyu's 
hanging out with three beautiful girls.</font>

226
00:11:36,630 --> 00:11:38,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure to correct them.</font>

227
00:11:41,810 --> 00:11:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But seriously.</font>

228
00:11:43,730 --> 00:11:46,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you all a thing?</font>

229
00:11:47,890 --> 00:11:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why would you...</font>

230
00:11:49,540 --> 00:11:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you're always together.</font>

231
00:11:51,650 --> 00:11:55,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sure a lot of people think 
you're with either Shio or Akari.</font>

232
00:12:00,550 --> 00:12:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like that...</font>

233
00:12:06,910 --> 00:12:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm, okay.</font>

234
00:12:09,540 --> 00:12:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah... right?</font>

235
00:12:11,670 --> 00:12:14,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can't be in a rom-com 
with your childhood friends...</i></font>

236
00:12:14,050 --> 00:12:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief.</font>

237
00:12:23,490 --> 00:12:25,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya, Haru-kun.</font>

238
00:12:25,310 --> 00:12:27,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's hang out next time!</font>

239
00:12:27,130 --> 00:12:28,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Kay!</font>

240
00:12:28,310 --> 00:12:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What did she mean by, "What a relief"?</i></font>

241
00:12:32,170 --> 00:12:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a relief.</font>

242
00:12:33,520 --> 00:12:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobody's cheating on anyone.</font>

243
00:12:36,750 --> 00:12:38,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, that can't be.</i></font>

244
00:12:39,180 --> 00:12:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Eiyu.</font>

245
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:44,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna go to that park after school 
where we used to play?</font>

246
00:12:44,330 --> 00:12:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sure.</font>

247
00:12:46,090 --> 00:12:48,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can invite Shio and Akari, too.</font>

248
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

249
00:12:52,160 --> 00:12:54,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want it to be just the two of us.</font>

250
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's still not here?</i></font>

251
00:13:03,380 --> 00:13:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why does she want to meet with me alone?</i></font>

252
00:13:06,520 --> 00:13:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, no, no! 
This is Haru we're talking about!</i></font>

253
00:13:09,790 --> 00:13:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why am I getting nervous?</i></font>

254
00:13:11,730 --> 00:13:12,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boo!</font>

255
00:13:13,700 --> 00:13:15,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You!</font>

256
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a great reaction!</font>

257
00:13:18,030 --> 00:13:20,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're early too, dude!</font>

258
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one riding a bike.</font>

259
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:24,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I didn't have any other plans.</font>

260
00:13:24,030 --> 00:13:26,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, wanna get started?</font>

261
00:13:26,410 --> 00:13:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get started on what?</font>

262
00:13:32,900 --> 00:13:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait!</font>

263
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:37,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

264
00:13:40,550 --> 00:13:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One-on-one, of course!</font>

265
00:13:46,210 --> 00:13:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on!</font>

266
00:13:47,970 --> 00:13:49,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show me what you've got!</font>

267
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:51,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your body the only thing 
that developed?!</font>

268
00:13:51,150 --> 00:13:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously? You just wanted 
to play basketball?</font>

269
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:55,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, of course!</font>

270
00:13:55,360 --> 00:13:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But yeah, what a relief!</font>

271
00:13:57,360 --> 00:13:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you all weren't a thing!</font>

272
00:13:59,080 --> 00:14:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why?</font>

273
00:14:00,670 --> 00:14:03,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because if you all were...</font>

274
00:14:04,610 --> 00:14:06,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We couldn't do this 
with just the two of us.</font>

275
00:14:10,370 --> 00:14:11,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha!</font>

276
00:14:15,750 --> 00:14:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang, you almost had it, too.</font>

277
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:20,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sh-Shut up!</font>

278
00:14:20,300 --> 00:14:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just rusty!</font>

279
00:14:24,510 --> 00:14:26,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could've scored if I tried.</font>

280
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here!</font>

281
00:14:27,010 --> 00:14:29,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, give me all you've got!</font>

282
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:32,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back then, you'd get physical 
just to steal the ball.</font>

283
00:14:34,140 --> 00:14:36,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what the heck happened, Haru?</font>

284
00:14:36,740 --> 00:14:38,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You suddenly stopped 
coming to the park.</font>

285
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:40,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were all waiting for you every day!</font>

286
00:14:40,530 --> 00:14:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad, I just got really busy.</font>

287
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know!</font>

288
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:49,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you got into 
the same high school as us!</font>

289
00:14:49,110 --> 00:14:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why didn't you tell us?!</font>

290
00:14:50,660 --> 00:14:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the ones who didn't 
even realize I'm a girl!</font>

291
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Haru hasn't changed.</i></font>

292
00:14:58,000 --> 00:15:00,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always messing with me.</i></font>

293
00:15:01,050 --> 00:15:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's definitely Haru!</i></font>

294
00:15:04,020 --> 00:15:05,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm not losing no matter what!</i></font>

295
00:15:22,380 --> 00:15:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First to three wins!</font>

296
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won!</font>

297
00:15:29,660 --> 00:15:32,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So soft... smells nice...</i></font>

298
00:15:32,090 --> 00:15:33,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it's </i>Haru<i>!</i></font>

299
00:15:33,410 --> 00:15:36,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Losers get what they get.</font>

300
00:15:36,240 --> 00:15:38,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? We never agreed on that!</font>

301
00:15:38,170 --> 00:15:40,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, this is how we always did it!</font>

302
00:15:40,070 --> 00:15:42,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What should it be?</font>

303
00:15:42,300 --> 00:15:45,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Isn't it always the forehead flick?</font>

304
00:15:46,490 --> 00:15:48,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I ask you a question instead?</font>

305
00:15:48,050 --> 00:15:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

306
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:54,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I actually heard about you guys 
going to the fireworks festival.</font>

307
00:15:57,760 --> 00:16:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shio and Akari confessed 
their love for you, right?</font>

308
00:16:01,940 --> 00:16:05,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're acting like 
nothing happened...</font>

309
00:16:06,250 --> 00:16:07,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu!</font>

310
00:16:07,290 --> 00:16:09,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you gonna choose?</font>

311
00:16:15,870 --> 00:16:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you talking about, Haru?</font>

312
00:16:19,590 --> 00:16:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, it may have looked that way to you.</font>

313
00:16:23,210 --> 00:16:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to disappoint you.</font>

314
00:16:25,050 --> 00:16:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

315
00:16:26,850 --> 00:16:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do see them that way, right? 
As more than friends?</font>

316
00:16:30,720 --> 00:16:33,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Not at all.</font>

317
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:34,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, I can tell.</font>

318
00:16:34,120 --> 00:16:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm your childhood friend, too.</font>

319
00:16:36,940 --> 00:16:39,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah, you were on a date 
with Runako, too.</font>

320
00:16:39,870 --> 00:16:41,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that about?</font>

321
00:16:41,730 --> 00:16:42,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

322
00:16:42,740 --> 00:16:44,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just spill it, Eiyu!</font>

323
00:16:44,730 --> 00:16:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you wanna start a rom-com 
with your childhood friends?</font>

324
00:16:49,740 --> 00:16:50,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's stupid!</font>

325
00:16:50,660 --> 00:16:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I could see my 
childhood friends as more than a friend!</font>

326
00:16:54,770 --> 00:16:56,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eiyu, do you remember?</font>

327
00:16:57,430 --> 00:16:59,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we graffitied 
that wall in our neighborhood?</font>

328
00:16:59,980 --> 00:17:00,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

329
00:17:00,870 --> 00:17:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brats!</font>

330
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When we got caught...</font>

331
00:17:03,500 --> 00:17:06,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're mistaken! It's the opposite! 
We were actually cleaning this wall!</font>

332
00:17:06,760 --> 00:17:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You told the most obvious lie.</font>

333
00:17:10,390 --> 00:17:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You totally have that same look now.</font>

334
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:15,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just admit it!</font>

335
00:17:15,140 --> 00:17:17,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I'm really not interested.</font>

336
00:17:17,020 --> 00:17:19,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Liar!</font>

337
00:17:19,240 --> 00:17:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enough of this crap. Let's go home.</font>

338
00:17:26,050 --> 00:17:27,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then fight me!</font>

339
00:17:27,780 --> 00:17:30,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you win, I won't bother you 
about it ever again.</font>

340
00:17:30,440 --> 00:17:34,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if I win, you have to 
tell me everything.</font>

341
00:17:34,090 --> 00:17:36,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? That's not fair.</font>

342
00:17:36,840 --> 00:17:39,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I'd agree to that.</font>

343
00:17:40,100 --> 00:17:41,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, please!</font>

344
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm so curious!</font>

345
00:17:43,340 --> 00:17:46,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't we friends?</font>

346
00:17:46,420 --> 00:17:48,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, come on, come on!</font>

347
00:17:48,730 --> 00:17:50,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jeez, cut the whining!</font>

348
00:17:50,850 --> 00:17:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, all right!</font>

349
00:17:52,180 --> 00:17:54,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But only under this condition!</font>

350
00:17:55,170 --> 00:17:57,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll only take you up on it 
if it's you-know-what.</font>

351
00:17:59,690 --> 00:18:00,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure thing.</font>

352
00:18:00,930 --> 00:18:02,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The current standing is eighty rounds,</font>

353
00:18:00,930 --> 00:18:01,850
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Comic Sans MS">80 Rounds</font></font></b></font>

354
00:18:00,930 --> 00:18:04,220
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Comic Sans MS">37 Wins</font></font></b></font>

355
00:18:01,730 --> 00:18:08,440
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Comic Sans MS">38 Losses</font></font></b></font>

356
00:18:02,470 --> 00:18:05,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">thirty-seven wins,
thirty-eight losses, five ties</font>

357
00:18:03,100 --> 00:18:08,440
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="32"><font face="Comic Sans MS">5 Ties</font></font></b></font>

358
00:18:05,530 --> 00:18:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and sure, I'm behind in wins...</font>

359
00:18:08,820 --> 00:18:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But since then, I haven't stopped training</font>

360
00:18:11,260 --> 00:18:13,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">even while brushing my teeth 
and taking baths...</font>

361
00:18:13,010 --> 00:18:15,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you think you can beat me?</font>

362
00:18:15,940 --> 00:18:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't talk smack
until you've won.</font>

363
00:18:19,050 --> 00:18:20,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

364
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:23,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Daruma-san! Daruma-san!</font>

365
00:18:23,300 --> 00:18:25,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time for the stare-down!</font>

366
00:18:25,050 --> 00:18:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Laugh and you lose!</font>

367
00:18:26,710 --> 00:18:28,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Na-na-na!</font>

368
00:18:30,840 --> 00:18:34,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You haven't gotten rusty at this, huh?</font>

369
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You too...</font>

370
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:38,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then!</font>

371
00:18:38,890 --> 00:18:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about this?!</font>

372
00:18:43,050 --> 00:18:44,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is that face?!</font>

373
00:18:44,660 --> 00:18:47,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Told you, I've been training!</font>

374
00:18:47,600 --> 00:18:48,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Behold!</font>

375
00:18:48,610 --> 00:18:52,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the new face 
I came up with just last week!</font>

376
00:18:53,490 --> 00:18:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Last week?</font>

377
00:18:55,380 --> 00:18:57,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been training even 
as a high-schooler?</font>

378
00:18:57,990 --> 00:19:01,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Shoot, I can't let that get me!</i></font>

379
00:19:01,370 --> 00:19:02,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But...</i></font>

380
00:19:02,500 --> 00:19:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My steel mask hardened by childhood 
friends isn't going to break easily!</i></font>

381
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:12,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come to think of it, 
I remember Shio asking about this.</font>

382
00:19:14,390 --> 00:19:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder if Eiyu likes someone.</font>

383
00:19:17,930 --> 00:19:19,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

384
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:25,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to come clean. Don't you think?</font>

385
00:19:25,440 --> 00:19:28,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You're being unfair, Haru!</font>

386
00:19:28,130 --> 00:19:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Akari's been quietly 
admiring you all along, too.</font>

387
00:19:32,130 --> 00:19:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You mean glaring?</font>

388
00:19:34,220 --> 00:19:36,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako's always said she likes you, too.</font>

389
00:19:36,980 --> 00:19:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's like a little sister!</font>

390
00:19:39,290 --> 00:19:41,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are you so stubborn about this?</font>

391
00:19:41,950 --> 00:19:45,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Back atcha. Why do you 
want to know so badly?</font>

392
00:19:45,580 --> 00:19:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you mean? That's obvious.</font>

393
00:19:48,530 --> 00:19:50,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to cheer you on!</font>

394
00:19:50,320 --> 00:19:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my dear childhood friend!</font>

395
00:19:53,640 --> 00:19:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haru...</font>

396
00:19:57,590 --> 00:19:59,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck is that face?</font>

397
00:19:59,710 --> 00:20:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not fair! Gosh!</font>

398
00:20:01,660 --> 00:20:02,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my normal face.</font>

399
00:20:03,850 --> 00:20:05,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I lost.</font>

400
00:20:06,470 --> 00:20:09,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. I trust you, Eiyu.</font>

401
00:20:09,240 --> 00:20:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do...</font>

402
00:20:12,900 --> 00:20:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do think of them 
as more than friends.</font>

403
00:20:16,830 --> 00:20:20,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure? I lost the bet.</font>

404
00:20:20,170 --> 00:20:23,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, you're a c-close 
friend of mine, Haru.</font>

405
00:20:26,200 --> 00:20:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah? Really? Ooh!</font>

406
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:29,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And? And?</font>

407
00:20:29,770 --> 00:20:31,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What exactly do you like about them?</font>

408
00:20:31,530 --> 00:20:32,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut up!</font>

409
00:20:33,020 --> 00:20:34,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is so embarrassing.</font>

410
00:20:34,860 --> 00:20:36,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno!</font>

411
00:20:36,180 --> 00:20:39,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not even sure if I'm really in love.</font>

412
00:20:39,010 --> 00:20:41,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel stupid seeing them 
as more than friends</font>

413
00:20:41,260 --> 00:20:43,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">when I don't know how they feel about me.</font>

414
00:20:43,940 --> 00:20:45,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

415
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so cute.</font>

416
00:20:55,330 --> 00:20:57,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what a complicated situation.</font>

417
00:20:57,780 --> 00:20:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll ask them for you!</font>

418
00:20:59,970 --> 00:21:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

419
00:21:02,050 --> 00:21:05,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be the one to support 
you guys' love life!</font>

420
00:21:06,980 --> 00:21:08,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}All right, let's go!</font>

421
00:21:07,870 --> 00:21:13,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font face="Arial"><b><font size="12"><font color="#fdffff">Episode 9</font></font></b></font></b></font>

422
00:21:08,040 --> 00:21:13,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fdfdfd">An Unfamiliar Girl Who's Your "Guy Friend"?</font></font></font></b></font>

423
00:21:08,830 --> 00:21:13,040
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Arial Black"><font color="#fdfdfd">But if You Laugh, It Still Won't Start a <font size="22"><font color="#10c7e6">Ro<font color="#f13d50">m-<font color="#9341b3">Co<font color="#f8a103">m</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

424
00:21:08,990 --> 00:21:10,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey! Hold up, wait!</font>

425
00:21:10,380 --> 00:21:12,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Just stay out of it!</font>

426
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:31,780
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<b><font color="#b5bace"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10">Translator:
Timer:
Editor:
Quality Control:
Final Quality Control:</font></font></font></b></b></font>

427
00:21:26,360 --> 00:21:31,780
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<b><font color="#b5bace"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="10">Sachiko Takahashi
Mariana Martinez
Gabriella Alabanza
S Bilyeu
Rei Miyasaka</font></font></font></b></b></font>

428
00:22:44,740 --> 00:22:46,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ready?</font>

429
00:22:49,100 --> 00:22:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Great to have you back, Haru-kun!</font>

430
00:22:51,270 --> 00:22:55,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We went all out today 
to celebrate our reunion!</font>

431
00:22:55,030 --> 00:22:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow. Thanks so much!</font>

432
00:22:58,120 --> 00:23:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm still shocked that you're a girl.</font>

433
00:23:01,830 --> 00:23:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Plus, you're cute and 
have an amazing figure!</font>

434
00:23:05,400 --> 00:23:07,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop it!</font>

435
00:23:07,030 --> 00:23:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two are really cute, too.</font>

436
00:23:09,970 --> 00:23:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah. How about Runako?</font>

437
00:23:11,950 --> 00:23:13,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's Runako?</font>

438
00:23:13,760 --> 00:23:14,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Runako's...</font>

439
00:23:14,730 --> 00:23:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't have to worry about Haru... right?</i></font>

440
00:23:17,820 --> 00:23:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen! Please stay out of this!</font>

441
00:23:20,460 --> 00:23:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? You embarrassed?</font>

442
00:23:23,290 --> 00:23:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can get them to open up 
about their feelings naturally.</font>

443
00:23:26,490 --> 00:23:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said you don't have to do that!</font>

444
00:23:29,640 --> 00:23:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We settled things with a pizza bun...</i></font>

445
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Delish!</i></font>

446
00:23:32,720 --> 00:23:34,390
<font size="24"><b>{\an8}<font color="#ec8fbc">Delish</font></b></font>

447
00:23:34,730 --> 00:23:36,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh yeah!</font>

448
00:23:36,410 --> 00:23:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was wondering, Shio and Akari...</font>

449
00:23:38,140 --> 00:23:38,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

450
00:23:38,760 --> 00:23:39,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

451
00:23:40,750 --> 00:23:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you two think about Eiyu?</font>

452
00:23:45,530 --> 00:23:46,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Idiot!</i></font>

